{"tid":209311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple TV 大陸下架諷刺中國節目　殃及港台　無國界記者譴責","createTime":"2017-04-20T06:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T11:16:30.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b00fb06fb90ea45b7178a16b9f982af86895e01d","tid":209311,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:18:24.000Z","msg":"| 立場報道 | 立場新聞<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/china-01_XQbp6_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fchina-01_XQbp6_1200x0.png&h=713dc6ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘋果的應用程式「Apple TV」早前將美國搞笑節目 China Uncensored 在中國大陸地區下架，連帶香港、台灣用戶亦無法觀看，引起爭議；新聞自由組織「無國界記者」發表聲明，譴責蘋果應中國當局要求，屏蔽該電視節目的決定。<br />\n<br />\n資訊科技界議員莫乃光亦在facebook發文，指AppleTV 今次下架波及港台，會否涉及審查或自我審查，促蘋果交代。<br />\n<br />\nChina Uncensored 由新唐人電視台製作，以惡搞中國新聞為主，但亦時有報道大陸維權人士的消息；2014 年香港爆發雨傘運動，該節目主持曾到香港採訪，亦曾訪問香港立法會議員梁國雄、台灣立法委員黃國昌等人。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本月 4 日，主持 Chris Chappell 在節目中宣佈，接獲蘋果通知，稱該節目因不符當地法規，將自中國大陸、香港及台灣版本的 App Stores 中移除，為此發起聯署向蘋果抗議。<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸目前為蘋果的第二大市場，超越歐洲。今年一月，《紐約時報》公佈，得悉蘋果公司已應中國大陸當局要求，將《紐約時報》中、英文版手機App，從中國大陸地區的 App Store移除。《紐約時報》發言人 Eileen Murphy 形容，中方的請求是阻止中國讀者閱讀獨立中國新聞之舉。"},{"pid":"1180df63ac99c9470e9415283fd34f1ebe077edb","tid":209311,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:20:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/apple-tv-大陸下架諷刺中國節目-殃及港台-無國界記者譴責/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2Fapple-tv-%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6%E8%AB%B7%E5%88%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE-%E6%AE%83%E5%8F%8A%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0-%E7%84%A1%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%8C%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%2F&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=c3688b63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2Fapple-tv-%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6%E8%AB%B7%E5%88%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE-%E6%AE%83%E5%8F%8A%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0-%E7%84%A1%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%8C%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%2F&h=04772b93\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/apple-tv-大陸下架諷刺中國節目-殃及港台-無國界記者譴責/</a>"},{"pid":"8c042a3e7920cef6abf934307549e66f16d76dd9","tid":209311,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:20:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9539a77847209dfd6ba17bced4d84456cbe17c87","tid":209311,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雜種"},{"pid":"79ff281d2bd0ebecb8d0e7015640d959bc48e9f4","tid":209311,"uid":20074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:21:20.000Z","msg":"唔屌中國政府<br />\n走去屌apple"},{"pid":"d84a540cc7cbede76886cb0df226c3069ce93068","tid":209311,"uid":42872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:21:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">China Uncensored 由新唐人電視台製作</span>"},{"pid":"b251e1cfd6499f70bacbe7f9ab990b6c8e7094bf","tid":209311,"uid":3007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1884210b47cacb4f17818bee01577f0ddb0dc58","tid":209311,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d2f9cfa809f6e437d9c8768ca93013f6f4a8fa","tid":209311,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔屌中國政府<br />\n走去屌apple</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢D組織永遠企係最安全地方做最安全既野"},{"pid":"1de07179fd8e217d8fb7d2a582d725aeb5f34397","tid":209311,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T07:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho